OL,6,FNusrat Ghani told ITV News Cornwall
OL,7,Fwould be the 'backbone' of the
OL,8,Fcountry's next economic revolution.
OL,10,FThe Minister for Industry and Economic
OL,11,FSecurity Nusrat Ghani MP has praised
OL,12,Fthe efforts of Cornwall's lithium
OL,13,Fextraction projects, saying the UK
OL,14,Fcan't achieve net zero without Cornish
