OL,4,CUK's economic success, says minister
OL,6,F"Once again Cornwall is going to be
OL,7,Fthe backbone of the next economic
OL,8,Frevolution in the UK."
OL,10,FCornish Lithium has been carrying out
OL,11,Ftest drilling on leased land at
OL,12,Fseveral sites.
OL,14,FAt Trelavour, on the outskirts of St
OL,15,FDennis, it plans to extract lithium
OL,16,Ffrom mica minerals within the granite
OL,17,Frock which underlies Cornwall.
