OL,6,FAt United Downs near Redruth, the
OL,7,Fcompany is aiming to produce battery
OL,8,Fquality zero carbon lithium chemicals
OL,9,Fdirectly from the geothermal waters 1-
OL,10,F2km underground.
OL,12,FCEO and Founder of Cornish Lithium
OL,13,FJeremy Wrathall told ITV News: "This
OL,14,Fproject alone at Trelavour will
OL,15,Fgenerate 300 jobs, and we've already
OL,16,Fcreated about 40 jobs here on site.
OL,18,F"We've had some evaluations done of
OL,19,Fthe total value add to Cornwall and
OL,20,Fthe UK from this project alone, which
OL,21,Fis around #800M.
