OL,3,CCornish mining will be 'backbone' of
OL,4,CUK's economic success, says minister
OL,6,F"It's a massive boost to the economy,
OL,7,Fand it also provides highly skilled
OL,8,Fjobs not seasonal jobs. We've got a
OL,9,Flot of graduates that work for us, it
OL,10,Freally is highly paid and highly
OL,11,Fskilled."
OL,13,FTest drilling at Trelavour was
OL,14,Fcompleted in 2023. The company now
OL,15,Fplans to open a demonstration plant in
OL,16,FMay, with the aim of commercial
OL,17,Fextraction beginning in 2027.
